title: Tim Hortons lobbied MPs for more temporary foreign workers over last 18 months
description: For more than a year, Canadian coffee giant Tim Hortons has been pushing the federal government to lift the cap on temporary foreign workers some of its franchisees can hire, CBC News has learned.
